<div id="review_2878021430" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2878021430" />
    <a title="Kevin R." class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/74062789-kevin-r"><img alt="Kevin R." src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2878021430?book_show_action=true">Aug 18, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kevin R." class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kevin R." href="/user/show/74062789-kevin-r">Kevin R.</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/19670343-thy-gold-to-refine">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2878021430" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1580255174511784164">This was a tough book to read. I already knew of the events that took place in this book (events surrounding the so-called &quot;Mormon War&quot; in Missouri) and there were no stories told that surprised me. But the events were brought to life in a way that they never had been before. Tears came to my eyes multiple times as I read this book. I don&apos;t even have words to describe the shock and sickening feeling that comes when one realized that the stories told in this book actually happened to real people.</span>
  <span id="freeText1580255174511784164" style="display:none">This was a tough book to read. I already knew of the events that took place in this book (events surrounding the so-called "Mormon War" in Missouri) and there were no stories told that surprised me. But the events were brought to life in a way that they never had been before. Tears came to my eyes multiple times as I read this book. I don't even have words to describe the shock and sickening feeling that comes when one realized that the stories told in this book actually happened to real people. To think of the merciless cruelty of the mobs is beyond comprehension. But people endured it. People came out of the forge with their faith stronger than ever. It's absolutely incredible.</span>
  <a data-text-id="1580255174511784164" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


