              <span id="reviewTextContainer2185789056" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13059419602960289977">I really enjoyed this book. This book laid out in detail the suffering and persecution that early members of the Mormon church faced. It was sad to read of all the terrible events. I feel that this historical fiction type of style is teaching me a lot about the history of the Mormon church. I am learning more than I have ever learned before and I really enjoy having a greater understanding of many of these events.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


